Package: NestedWGCNA
Title: Minimal Two-Stage Gene Co-Expression Analysis
Version: 1.00
Author: Dai [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Dai <dai@example.com>
Description: Minimal and computation-focused implementation of a two-stage
    gene co-expression workflow. The package computes gene adjacency and
    dissimilarity, identifies coarse-grained modules, derives core genes,
    normalizes expression by module cores, and identifies fine-grained modules.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/dai540/NestedWGCNA,
    https://dai540.github.io/NestedWGCNA/
BugReports: https://github.com/dai540/NestedWGCNA/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests:
